annotationA: DNA polymerase subunit gamma-1, mitochondrial; Involved in the replication of mitochondrial DNA. Has both 5'-3' DNA polymerase and 3'-5' exonuclease activity
annotationB: Mitochondrial transcription factor A is essential for mtDNA transcription and replication. It also binds to mtDNA nonspecifically, and plays a role in mtDNA maintenance by packaging mtDNA
